objects. The third effect can be used to propose a\nnon-cosmological explanation of high redshifts of quasars and gamma-ray bursts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 May 2007 22:55:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 15 Oct 2007 21:02:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2008-11-26"}
